Class AbstractRowProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query.row.AbstractRowProvider
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DecomposedQueryRangeRowProvider

    public abstract class AbstractRowProvider
extends Object
    This is a simple abstraction on providing the next row to skip for the RowProviderSkippingIterator to act on. It at least handles setting the current row to a member variable.
